data.content:
Danh từ
người chăn bò
cao bồi
(Anh, khẩu ngữ) lái buôn xảo trá; kẻ bất tài lừa lọc
the house has all these defects because it was built by cowboys
ngôi nhà bị tất cả các khuyết tật đó là vì nó được tụi bất tài lừa lọc xây dựng lên

noun
plural -boys
[count] a man who rides a horse and whose job is to take care of cows or horses especially in the western U.S.
a movie about cowboys in the old West
He worked for several years as a cowboy on a ranch in Texas.
a man who performs in a rodeo
usually disapproving :someone who has qualities that are commonly associated with the cowboys in movies especially; :someone who does things that other people consider foolish and dangerous
political cowboys
We've got a bunch of risk-taking cowboys running this project. - sometimes used before another noun
cowboy diplomacy
verb
-boys; -boyed; -boying
[no obj] US :to work as a cowboy
He cowboyed in Texas and Oklahoma.
